data.description:
Everything you need in a home, right here on Relich Ave. The all new master suite in this home is like no other; huge master bedroom with a cathredral ceiling, recessed LED lights, and a massive walk in closet. Spacious master bath with a deep soaking tub, tiled heated  floor and stand up shower.  All new vinyl flooring and freshly painted throughout, the home. Updated first floor bathroom. All new light fixtures and LED lights in all bedrooms. Tear off roof, all electrical, and plumbing done in 2020. Shed and concrete driveway done in 2020, and windows are all updated since 2020 or 2023. 
Square footage number based on measurement done by a licensed appraiser of all finished space.
